<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">   <!-- lang passato da app -->
    <head>
        <title></title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Hello {{ name }}!</h1>
        
        <p>
            We received a request to reset the password for the user with this email address. 
            To reset the password, please click <a href="http://{{ app.request.getHost() }}/#/reset/{{ hash }}">here</a> or 
            copy the following link into the address bar of your browser and reset the password. <br>
            http://{{ app.request.getHost() }}/#/reset/{{ hash }}
        </p>
        
        <p>
            You have 24 hours to reset the password, afterwards you'll have to request a new link.<br>
            If you did not request to reset the password yourself, please ignore this email.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            Best regards,<br>
            the GeoBI-team.
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
